My Second serious map, took about 2 weeks to make this map. 

Bomb site in middle, sniper locations covering it from all angles. Bomb site is on the bridge over a large chasm, with two smaller bridges on either side. However, the two small bridges are rigged with explosives and will blow if triggered by another player.

Plenty of cover from snipers in open area and lots of room to move.

No I do not want a nav file.

One texturing mistake, however, i'm to lazy to re-compile the whole thing over it. Other than that, I hope someone will enjoy this map.

Port from Counter-Strike: Global Offensive to Counter-Strike: Source, of Radix's famous map, de_austria. This port was made with Radix's indirect permission, provided by Nikosemen, who also provided the original VMF which I used to port and improve the map.

In-game map name: de_csgoaustria

Features:
- HDR and LDR compatible.
- Working radar
- Working soundscapes
- Working bot navigation (original CSGO file)
- Working custom particles (chimney smoke, etc)
- Working cubemaps
- Improved shadows

As it is, this port is identical to how it is in CSGO. No glitches or anything as far as I know, and no compromises. A perfect port.

Special thanks to Gondallez for writing a particle converter.
